Create vnenv : 
py -m venv myenv

Start Env : 
myenv/scripts/activate

install django : 
pip install django

create project: 
py -m django startproject myproject .

run project : 
py manage.py runserver

create app : 
py manage.py startapp myapp

Register app in settings.py in project : 
INSTALLED_APPS = [
    ''
]

----
project - >url.py [include]

----
app - urls.py [import view - > create view] 